data.description: MLS# 273217 Discover the enchantment of this captivating "F" house nestled in a serene central Richland neighborhood with irresistible curb appeal! Immerse yourself in the perfect fusion of historic charm and contemporary comforts as this meticulously updated home showcases its original hardwood floors.Fall in love with the bright and spacious living room, adorned with a rustic accent wall and a gas stove, creating an inviting atmosphere for cozy fall and winter gatherings. The formal dining space features a ship lap accent ceiling, adding a touch of elegance to your dining experience.The light-filled kitchen is a chef's delight, boasting tile flooring, butcher block countertops, a pantry, updated appliances, and a garden window that brings the outdoors in. Upstairs, three charming bedrooms await, accompanied by a full bath, while the basement offers an additional half bath, a large family room, a laundry room, and a versatile flex room, perfect for an office or workout space.Step into the dreamy backyard oasis, fully fenced for privacy, and featuring a covered deck with an eating bar. Immerse yourself in the in-ground swimming pool, surrounded by an expansive patio space, a built-in kitchen/bar, mature landscaping, shade trees, and ample room for a garden. Completing the outdoor experience are a detached garage and a garden shed. Call your favorite realtor for a showing!
